  "description": "Adds a laboratory structure with 5 loot chests.",
  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">Please note that for this mod to work you will need to install both cobblemon and my resource lib.</span></h2>\n<hr>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Cobblemon : Poke Lab's</h1>\n<p>◽ Adds a rare structure, with apparatus for healing and handling your pokemons, and 5 loot chests.<br>◽ Adds a slight improvement to the loot in the game's chests</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_f7701d80-2f75-4955-a0e6-843ce19770af.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_08caadc5-0be4-46e2-b006-3aec87200794.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_050be908-3c00-46b5-acad-6f35724bf5a2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"338\" height=\"362\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_84c5339a-cab7-49b7-be04-09735449a5e7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"380\" height=\"363\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">MODEL CREDITS : @<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/webslinger2203/\" rel=\"nofollow\">webslinger2203</a><br><br><br></h3>",
